{"tid":753641,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「有圖，已多人中伏」想完子華夢，都要比人呃！","createTime":"2018-07-23T18:42:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T12:53:50.000Z","uid":15894,"like":12,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ed72b430389a62e1095ce59a44e21aaba515c810","tid":753641,"uid":15894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T18:42:35.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，話說之前係隔離個 「黃子華放/交換post」留左個tg收飛。<br />\n隔左無幾耐就有位巴打就話放$480張飛，正當我滿心歡喜唔洗硬食黃牛之際，條友仔就嚟料！<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/24/023557_d2d92988a948e21c1846673696a24e63.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F24%2F023557_d2d92988a948e21c1846673696a24e63.png&h=fcb19907&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/24/023558_b406aef0ab3a43b5fb3ef8154afe5edd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F24%2F023558_b406aef0ab3a43b5fb3ef8154afe5edd.png&h=200cc72f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/24/023559_1ba02e47a2c70495709121a8eb026aeb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F24%2F023559_1ba02e47a2c70495709121a8eb026aeb.png&h=31214844&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/24/023600_816ac6aefc7e70118102265e4d2eaf2f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F24%2F023600_816ac6aefc7e70118102265e4d2eaf2f.png&h=94b069e1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/24/023601_dde059cf4c2765dabb0e7c9e88353aa0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F24%2F023601_dde059cf4c2765dabb0e7c9e88353aa0.png&h=5b1e8020&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好彩小弟發現寄件地點係香港，覺得有古怪先無中伏！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fa